	   <tr><td colspan=2>All combat related skills (weapons, offense, defense, double attack, etc.) cap at 200 for paladins at level 40.<br><br>At level 51, these skills will begin to raise again.&nbsp;&nbsp;Offense caps at 210 for sure and defense at 227 (no skill increases I'm told at level 60, bummer).<br><br>Magical skills cap higher than our melee skills, as far as I've seen.  The exception being defense, because we are more defensive hybrids (or something, it's late, sue me).<br><br>I hope this helps.<br>&nbsp;<br><b>Praetor</b>, 60th Crusader<br>Avatars of Discord</td></tr>
