	   <tr><td colspan=2>Dear Anonymous,<br><br>It sounds to me as if a little more study at the guild hall is in order. &lt;sympathetic smile&gt;<br><br>However, the answers to your questions are as follows.&nbsp;&nbsp;Paladin's can not make any magic, cast in any way, until level nine.  (Of course, we have the healing ability, "lay hand" beginning at our initiation into the guild.)  Hence no mana until then.  Level nine is also when we can memorize our first healing spell.  The same spell, by the way, that clerics receive at level one.  &lt;thoughtful look&gt;<br><br>Paladins, as all classes, receive 5 opportunities for practice at every level.  Use them wisely.<br><br>Blessing upon you as you pursue the high calling.<br><br>Nidala of Lanys<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
