	   <tr><td colspan=2>High Elves make fine Paladins eventually, but it requires a lot of STR enhancing items to make it happen.&nbsp;&nbsp;STR is the most important stat for any tank class, and HE's don't start with much of it.<br><br>Starting off in life, HE Paladins are much more difficulte than a Dwarf Paladin.  The extra 35 STR the Dwarves get naturally makes it possible for them to wear a full suit of bronze armor without becoming encumbered.  The only problem Dwarves have starting off is low AGI.  Getting AGI above 75 will add 33 AC, which is huge.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
	   <span style='font-weight: normal; font-size: 9px;'>[<a href=#top>Top</a>]</span></tr>
