	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Heavens no, don't start over!&nbsp;&nbsp;While a STR of 100 is really low for a tank, any stat deficit can be fixed with items.  And there are LOTS of items to increase STR!<br><br>Get a Spiked Collar (+3 STR), a Purity Belt (+2 STR), Golden Amber earrings (+3 STR each), Jagged Bands (+3 str each), Bloodstained Mantle (+3 STR) and a Cracked Darkwood Shield (+9 STR) to start.  This will add +29 STR for around 300pp.<br><br>STR well above 100 will make your life *much* easier.  You can carry heavy armor and weapons with out becoming encumbered, which will allow you to hit harder and not get hit as often.  You will also start to see damage bonuses for STR above 100 now that you are above level 20, so get all the STR you can.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
